TEAM — Perceptive Advisors








































 INVESTMENT TEAMTRADING OPERATIONS TEAMCommitted to Fueling InnovationThe Perceptive team operates with integrity and adheres to the highest set of ethical principles. Our team offers a wealth of industry knowledge with degrees that range from science and medicine to mechanical engineering and finance. We are passionately committed to identifying innovative companies that can drive meaningful change.  The Perceptive team has a long and successful track record investing in the life sciences industry.  © 2016 Perceptive Advisors, LLC • 51 Astor Place, 10th Floor • New York, New York, 10003 • (646) 205-5340Disclaimer • Online Privacy Policy • Terms and ConditionsSite designed by Case Study Brands


















