OUR DNA — Perceptive Advisors
















































It is not the strongest of the species that survives, nor the most intelligent, but the one most responsive to change. Fueling Innovation in Life SciencesFounded in 1999, Perceptive Advisors is focused on supporting the progress of the life sciences industry by identifying opportunities and directing financial resources to the most promising technologies in healthcare. Our dedicated team of industry experts uses a unique balance of scientific, technical and investment expertise to identify opportunities. We seek to evaluate opportunities without biases by analyzing and weighing critical data and catalysts assessing the balance between market perception and reality. Perceptive manages approximately $2 billion across our strategies and has a long and successful track record.







POINT OF VIEWCommitted to Industry InnovationPerceptive is exclusively focused on the healthcare sector including biotech, life sciences, diagnostics, medical devices and healthcare services. Our goal is to identify companies on the cusp of breakthroughs in the understanding, diagnosis, and treatment of important unmet medical needs. We employ rigorous evaluation, and fundamental analysis to adapt to meet an ever-changing landscape. Perceptive’s team-based iterative process centers on critical evaluation of every idea with a strong focus on risk management.  > Learn more about our philosophy on investing.







 







 PASSIONDiscovering Investment OpportunitiesThe Perceptive team is committed to making game-changing contributions by identifying and helping bring forward the most promising innovations in the life sciences industry. It is this passion to drive life changing advancements that keep the Perceptive team focused intently on uncovering compelling investment opportunities.  > Learn more about our investments.







PEOPLEA Well-Rounded Research EngineThe Perceptive team has unique depth and breadth of industry expertise and knowledge. Our team includes trained scientists, molecular biologists, engineers and PhDs, dedicated to identifying trends, technologies and underappreciated assets in the life sciences industry. Our team has also worked together consistently over the years providing great stability and continuity.> Learn more about the Perceptive team. © 2016 Perceptive Advisors, LLC • 51 Astor Place, 10th Floor • New York, New York, 10003 • (646) 205-5340 Disclaimer • Online Privacy Policy • Terms and ConditionsSite designed by Case Study Brands


















